          "text": "I now have the official Bootstrap alerts documentation. The key points are:\n\n1. **Basic alerts**: `<div class=\"alert alert-{color}\" role=\"alert\">content</div>`\n2. **Link color**: Use `.alert-link` class on links\n3. **Additional content**: Can include headings (`.alert-heading`), paragraphs, dividers (`<hr>`), etc.\n4. **Icons**: Alerts with icons use `d-flex align-items-center` and SVG icons\n5. **Dismissible**: Add `.alert-dismissible` class + close button with `data-bs-dismiss=\"alert\"` + `.fade .show` classes\n\nLet me now read more component documentation files to understand what else needs to be updated. I'll start with badges, buttons, card, etc.\n",
