          "text": "Let me analyze the conversation history to create an anchored summary.\n\n**Goal:** \nBuild a k1.lib-bootstrap library for Bootstrap 5 components in PHP, implementing all official Bootstrap components with proper documentation and a demo showcase.\n\n**Constraints & Preferences:**\n- Namespace changed from `k1\\lib` to `k1lib`\n- Use `append_child()` for adding children, avoid `prepend_child()` as it doesn't exist\n- Components should match official Bootstrap v5.3.8 docs exactly\n- All files should have DocBlock headers with author, link, license, and version info\n- BETA components should have `@version BETA` in DocBlock\n\n**Progress:**\n\nDone:\n- Created GitHub repo klan1/k1.lib-bootstrap\n- Restructured src to src/klan1/html/bootstrap\n- Updated composer.json autoload path\n- Added docblocks to all existing files\n- Created 17 BETA component proposals (alert, badge, breadcrumb, button_group, card, carousel, collapse, dropdown, list_group, nav, navbar, pagination, progress, spinner, toast, offcanvas, tooltip)\n- Created demo/index.php showcase page\n- Added composer demo script\n- Fixed namespace conflicts in demo\n- Fixed alert close button position (top-right, position-absolute)\n- Fixed alert class structure (alert-dismissible fade show position-relative)\n- Fixed callout to use set_value() for string content\n- Fixed badge to use text-bg-* instead of bg-*\n- Fixed card structure\n\nIn Progress:\n- Reading Bootstrap v5.3.8 docs and fixing all components to match official docs\n\nBlocked:\n- (none)\n\n**Key Decisions:**\n- Changed namespace from `k1\\lib` to `k1lib` to fix autoload issues\n- Using `set_value()` for string content instead of `append_child()` which requires tag objects\n- Using `btn-close position-absolute top-0 end-0` for close button positioning\n\n\n- Applying `text-bg-*` pattern for color variants\n\n**Next Steps:**\n- Fix breadcrumb, button_group, carousel, collapse, dropdown, list_group, modal, nav/navbar, offcanvas, pagination, progress, spinner, toast, tooltip\n- Fix grid, menu, table and other existing components\n- Update demo to reflect all component changes\n- Update documentation in README\n\n**Critical Context:**\n- Bootstrap 5.3.8 uses text-bg-* for badges (not bg-*)\n- Close button needs position-absolute top-0 end-0\n- append_child() requires tag objects, not strings\n- prepend_child() does not exist\n- alert needs alert-dismissible fade show position-relative classes for dismissible variants\n\n**Relevant Files:**\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/*.php - Component classes\n- demo/index.php - Showcase page\n- composer.json - Package config\n",
