        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "\n\n## Goal\nBuild a PHP library (k1.lib-bootstrap) for Bootstrap 5 components with proper documentation, demo showcase, and full compliance with official Bootstrap v5.3.8 documentation.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Namespace: `k1lib` (changed from `k1\\lib` to fix autoload)\n- Use `append_child()` only (no `prepend_child` - doesn't exist)\n- Use `set_value()` for string content (append_child requires tag objects)\n- Close button: `btn-close position-absolute top-0 end-0`\n- All files need DocBlock with author, link, license, version\n- BETA components: add `@version BETA` to DocBlock\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Created GitHub repo klan1/k1.lib-bootstrap\n- Restructured src to src/klan1/html/bootstrap\n- Created 17 BETA component proposals\n- Created demo/index.php interactive showcase\n- Added composer demo script\n- Fixed alert: close button position, alert-dismissible classes\n- Fixed badge: text-bg-* (Bootstrap 5.2+ standard)\n- Fixed card: simplified structure, optional header/footer\n\n### In Progress\n- Reading Bootstrap v5.3.8 docs and fixing all components to match official documentation\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Namespace changed from `k1\\lib` to `k1lib` to resolve autoload conflicts\n- Using set_value() for string content instead of append_child()\n- Close button uses Bootstrap 5 utility classes for positioning\n\n## Next Steps\n- Fix breadcrumb, button_group, carousel, collapse, dropdown\n- Fix list_group, modal, nav, navbar, offcanvas\n- Fix pagination, progress, spinner, toast, tooltip\n- Fix grid, menu, table, and other existing components\n- Update demo to reflect all changes\n- Update README documentation\n\n## Critical Context\n- Bootstrap 5.3.8 uses text-bg-* for badges (not bg-*)\n- Dismissible alert needs: alert-dismissible fade show position-relative\n- append_child() requires tag objects, not strings\n\n## Relevant Files\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/*.php - Component classes\n- demo/index.php - Interactive showcase page\n- composer.json - Package config with demo script\n- vendor/klan1/k1lib.html - Dependency base library",
