          "text": "The user wants me to update the button_group.php file to reference the buttons.mdx specification, but the buttons.mdx file is about buttons, not button groups. The button_group is about grouping buttons together, so it should still reference button-group.mdx.\n\nWait, let me re-read the request. The user says \"use the https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/v5.3.8/site/src/content/docs/components/buttons.mdx specification for the buttons sent to the group\"\n\nSo the user wants me to add a note in the DocBlock that the buttons within the group follow the buttons.mdx specification. This makes sense since button_group contains buttons, and buttons follow the buttons component spec.\n\nLet me fetch the buttons.mdx to understand what it contains, then update the button_group.php DocBlock.\n",
