            "output": "  k1.lib-bootstrap - Components Showcase   \n\n[k1.lib-bootstrap](#) Bootstrap 5 Components\n\nComponents [Button](#button) [Badge](#badge) [Breadcrumb](#breadcrumb) [Button Group](#button-group) [Card](#card) [Callout](#callout) [Collapse](#collapse) [Dropdown](#dropdown) [Grid](#grid) [List Group](#list-group) [Menu](#menu) [Modal](#modal) [Nav](#nav) [Navbar](#navbar) [Pagination](#pagination) [Progress](#progress) [Spinner](#spinner) [Table](#table) [Toast](#toast) [Title Bar](#title-bar) [Top Bar](#top-bar)\n\n## Button\n\nPreview\n\n###### Variants\n\nPrimary Secondary Success Danger Warning Info Light Dark Link\n\n###### Outline\n\nPrimary Secondary Success Danger Warning Info Light Dark\n\n###### Sizes\n\nLarge Default Small\n\n###### States\n\nDisabled Active Toggle\n\nPHP\n\n```\n// Basic button\n$btn = new button('Click me', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY);\n\n// Outline variant\n$btn = new button('Outline', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY, button::SIZE_MD, true);\n\n// Disabled state\n$btn = new button('Disabled');\n$btn->set_disabled();\n\necho $btn->generate();\n```\n\n## Alert\n\nPreview\n\nA simple primary alert—check it out!\n\nA simple secondary alert—check it out!\n\nA simple success alert—check it out!\n\nA simple danger alert—check it out!\n\nA simple warning alert—check it out!\n\nA simple info alert—check it out!\n\nA simple light alert—check it out!\n\nA simple dark alert—check it out!\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$alert = new alert('This is an alert!', 'primary', true);\necho $alert->generate();\n```\n\n## Badge\n\nPreview\n\nPrimary Secondary Success Danger Warning Info Light Dark Pill Badge\n\nPHP\n\n```\necho (new badge('Primary'))->generate() . ' ';\necho (new badge('Secondary', 'secondary'))->generate();\necho (new badge('Pill', 'primary', true))->generate();\n```\n\n## Breadcrumb\n\nPreview\n\n1.  [Home](#)\n2.  [Library](#)\n3.  [Data](#)\n4.  Current Page\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$bread = new breadcrumb([\n    ['text' => 'Home', 'href' => '#'],\n    ['text' => 'Library', 'href' => '#'],\n    ['text' => 'Current Page']\n]);\necho $bread->generate();\n```\n\n## Button Group\n\nPreview\n\n###### Basic\n\nLeft Center Right\n\n###### Sizes\n\nSmall Small\n\nLarge Large\n\n###### Vertical\n\nTop Middle Bottom\n\nPHP\n\n```\n// Basic group\n$group = new button_group();\n$group->add_button(new button('Left', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY))\n      ->add_button(new button('Center', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY))\n      ->add_button(new button('Right', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY));\n\n// Access buttons\n$group->button(0); // Returns first button\n```\n\n## Card\n\nPreview\n\n##### Card Title\n\n###### Card Subtitle\n\nSome quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.\n\nGo somewhere\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$card = new card(\n    'Card Title',\n    'Card Subtitle',\n    'Card content text'\n);\n$card->body()->append_child(\n    new button('Go somewhere', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY)\n);\necho $card->generate();\n```\n\n## Callout\n\nPreview\n\n###### Callout Title\n\nThis is a dismissible callout message.\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$callout = new callout(\n    'This is a callout message.',\n    'Callout Title',\n    true,\n    'primary'\n);\necho $callout->generate();\n```\n\n## Collapse\n\nPreview\n\nToggle Content\n\nThis is collapsible content.\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$trigger = new button('Toggle', button::VARIANT_PRIMARY);\n$collapse = new collapse('demo', $trigger, 'Content');\necho $collapse->generate();\n```\n\n## Dropdown\n\nPreview\n\nActions\n\n-   [Action](#)\n-   [Another Action](#)\n\n-   [Separated Link](#)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$dropdown = new dropdown('Actions', [\n    ['text' => 'Action', 'href' => '#'],\n    ['divider' => true],\n    ['text' => 'Separated', 'href' => '#']\n]);\necho $dropdown->generate();\n```\n\n## Grid\n\nPreview\n\nRow 1, Col 1\n\nRow 1, Col 2\n\nRow 1, Col 3\n\nRow 2, Col 1\n\nRow 2, Col 2\n\nRow 2, Col 3\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$grid = new grid(2, 3);\n$row1 = $grid->row(1);\n$row1->general(4)->small(6);\n$row1->get_child(0)->set_value('Col 1');\necho $grid->generate();\n```\n\n## List Group\n\nPreview\n\n-   [First item](#)\n-   [Second item](#)\n-   [Third item](#)\n-   Disabled item\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$list = new list_group([\n    ['text' => 'First item', 'href' => '#'],\n    ['text' => 'Second', 'active' => true],\n    ['text' => 'Third', 'href' => '#']\n]);\necho $list->generate();\n```\n\n## Menu\n\nPreview\n\n-   [Home](#)\n-   [About](#)\n-   [Services](#)\n-   [Contact](#)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$menu = new menu('dropdown');\n$menu->add_menu_item('#', 'Home');\n$menu->add_menu_item('#', 'About');\necho $menu->generate();\n```\n\n## Modal\n\nPreview\n\n# Modal Title\n\nThis is the modal body content.\n\nCancel Confirm\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$modal = new modal(\n    'Modal Title',\n    'Content',\n    'Cancel',\n    'Confirm'\n);\necho $modal->generate();\n```\n\n## Nav\n\nPreview\n\n-   nav-item [Home](#)\n-   nav-item [Features](#)\n-   nav-item [Pricing](#)\n-   nav-item [Disabled](#)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$nav = new nav([\n    ['text' => 'Home', 'active' => true],\n    ['text' => 'Features', 'href' => '#']\n], 'pills');\necho $nav->generate();\n```\n\n## Navbar\n\nPreview\n\n[Brand Name](#)\n\n-   nav-item [Home](#)\n-   nav-item [Link](#)\n-   nav-item [Dropdown](#)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$navbar = new navbar('Brand', 'demoNav', 'light');\n$nav = new nav([...], 'nav');\n$navbar->add_to_collapse($nav);\necho $navbar->generate();\n```\n\n## Pagination\n\nPreview\n\n-   [«](/page?page=2)\n-   [1](/page?page=1)\n-   [2](/page?page=2)\n-   [3](/page?page=3) (current)\n-   [4](/page?page=4)\n-   [5](/page?page=5)\n-   [6](/page?page=6)\n-   [7](/page?page=7)\n-   [8](/page?page=8)\n-   [9](/page?page=9)\n-   [10](/page?page=10)\n-   [»](/page?page=4)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$pager = new pagination(3, 10, '/page', true);\necho $pager->generate();\n```\n\n## Progress\n\nPreview\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$prog = new progress([\n    ['value' => 25, 'type' => 'primary'],\n    ['value' => 50, 'striped' => true]\n], 20);\necho $prog->generate();\n```\n\n## Spinner\n\nPreview\n\n  \n  \n\nPHP\n\n```\n// Border spinner\necho (new spinner('border', 'primary'))->generate();\n\n// Grow spinner\necho (new spinner('grow', 'success'))->generate();\n```\n\n## Table\n\nPreview\n\n1\n\nJohn Doe\n\njohn@example.com\n\nAdmin\n\n2\n\nJane Smith\n\njane@example.com\n\nEditor\n\n3\n\nBob Wilson\n\nbob@example.com\n\nUser\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$table = new table_from_data();\n$table->set_data([\n    ['id' => 1, 'name' => 'John'],\n    ['id' => 2, 'name' => 'Jane']\n]);\necho $table->generate();\n```\n\n## Toast\n\nPreview\n\n×\n\nThis is the toast body message.\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$toast = new toast(\n    'Header',\n    'Body message',\n    true,\n    5000\n);\necho $toast->generate();\n```\n\n## Title Bar\n\nPreview\n\nPage Title\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$title = new title_bar('demo');\n$title->title()->set_value('Page Title');\necho $title->generate();\n```\n\n## Top Bar\n\nPreview\n\n-   My Application\n-   [Home](#)\n-   [About](#)\n-   [Services](#)\n-   [Contact](#)\n\nPHP\n\n```\n$top = new top_bar('main');\n$top->title()->set_value('My App');\n$top->menu_left()->add_menu_item('#', 'Home');\necho $top->generate();\n```",
