r official specs\n\n## Next Steps\n- Fix modal component using getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/components/modal/ specs\n- Test all demo sections for proper rendering\n- Review other components for method chaining pattern\n\n## Critical Context\n- Modal not working - needs investigation\n- `span` constructor doesn't accept value as 3rd arg - use `set_value()`\n- Button constants: VARIANT_PRIMARY, VARIANT_SECONDARY, VARIANT_SUCCESS, VARIANT_DANGER, VARIANT_WARNING, VARIANT_INFO, VARIANT_LIGHT, VARIANT_DARK, VARIANT_LINK\n- Button sizes: SIZE_SM, SIZE_MD, SIZE_LG\n- list-group-item-action class required for hover/active states\n\n## Relevant Files\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/button.php: Bootstrap button with variants, sizes, states\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/button_group.php: Method chaining API (add_button, button, count, remove_button)\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/breadcrumb.php: Method chaining API (add_item, item, count, remove_item)\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/toast.php: Fixed span value issue\n- src/klan1/html/bootstrap/list_group.php: Fixed active state styling\n- demo/index.php: Interactive showcase with Bootstrap standard design\n- getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/components/modal/: Official modal documentation",
